Miscellaneous Highlights: The second ODI match between South Africa and Ireland will be played on Friday, October 4, 2024, at the Jaidah Cricket Stadium in Abu Dhabi.
The match will start at 5 PM Indian Standard Time (IST) and the toss will take place 30 minutes prior to that.
The match will not be broadcast on TV in India, but it will be live streamed on the FanCode app and website.
